### 社团管理系统API测试文件
### 使用IntelliJ IDEA或VS Code的REST Client插件运行

### 1. 系统信息
GET http://localhost:8080/api/system/info

### 2. 健康检查
GET http://localhost:8080/api/system/health

### 3. 用户注册
POST http://localhost:8080/api/usr/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "passwordHash": "5d41402abc4b2a76b9719d911017c592",
  "gender": 1
}

### 4. 用户登录
POST http://localhost:8080/api/usr/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "passwordHash": "5d41402abc4b2a76b9719d911017c592"
}

### 5. 高级注册（创建老师账号）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/usr/reg_plus
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "teacher1",
  "passwordHash": "5d41402abc4b2a76b9719d911017c592",
  "gender": 1,
  "roleId": 3,
  "operatorUserId": 1
}

### 6. 创建社团
POST http://localhost:8080/api/club/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "计算机协会",
  "description": "计算机技术交流社团",
  "presidentId": 1,
  "teacherId": 2,
  "memberIds": [1, 2],
  "operatorUserId": 1
}

### 7. 获取所有社团
GET http://localhost:8080/api/club/all

### 8. 申请加入社团
POST http://localhost:8080/api/club/join
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 3,
  "clubId": 1
}

### 9. 创建活动
POST http://localhost:8080/api/activity/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clubId": 1,
  "creatorId": 1,
  "title": "编程竞赛",
  "description": "年度编程竞赛活动",
  "startTime": "2024-12-01T09:00:00",
  "endTime": "2024-12-01T17:00:00"
}

### 10. 获取所有活动
GET http://localhost:8080/api/activity/all

### 11. 获取社团活动列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/activity/club/1

### 12. 获取正在进行的活动
GET http://localhost:8080/api/activity/ongoing

### 13. 获取所有用户
GET http://localhost:8080/api/usr/all?page=1&size=10

### 14. 根据身份获取用户
